paper_metadata.title: MAIN TEXT
paper_metadata.extraction_summary: The paper discusses the presence of a circulating KCNH2 channel activator in patients with heart failure and ventricular tachyarrhythmias, but does not report specific genetic variants in the KCNH2 gene.

challenges: The paper did not mention specific genetic variants in the KCNH2 gene.
extraction_metadata.notes: The paper focused on the functional effects of a circulating factor on KCNH2 currents rather than specific genetic variants.
